    public abstract class GeneratorImpl
extends org.eclipse.emf.ecore.impl.MinimalEObjectImpl.Container
implements Generator
    An implementation of the model object 'Generator'.

    The following features are implemented:

    • Tuple Root
    • Generator Feature Modes
    • Remarks
    • Footprint Nof Vars
    • Footprint Nof Cons
    • Footprint Nof Terms
    • Count Cons
    • Count Vars
    • ELp Var Count
    • ELp Cons Count
    • Code
    • Solution Provider
    • Selected
    • Goals
